Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Illegal immigration, 1981
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wjkg
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Sep 1981
Presidents of US and Mexico to discuss growing problem of illegal immigrants. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.